00:00:22.630 --> 00:00:25.200
&gt;&gt; T.J. Halstead: Good morning.

00:00:25.200 --> 00:00:27.180
I'm T.J. Halstead,
the Deputy Director

00:00:27.180 --> 00:00:30.230
of the Congressional Research
Service, and it is my pleasure

00:00:30.230 --> 00:00:33.060
