00:06:23.800 --> 00:06:27.790
So it's as good a time as any to
take stock of where we've been

00:06:27.790 --> 00:06:31.910
and where we may be headed as a
new Administration takes power here

00:06:31.910 --> 00:06:34.710
in Washington.

00:06:34.710 --> 00:06:37.190
Now under the new rules of
the House of Representatives,

00:06:37.190 --> 00:06:40.330
all legislation we
introduce must be accompanied

00:06:40.330 --> 00:06:42.320
by a statement naming
